5. Security Model

5.1 Deterministic Policy Enforcement

No probabilistic AI gating in MVP.

Determinism ensures:
	•	Audit reproducibility
	•	Regulatory clarity
	•	Conflict resolution capability

⸻

5.2 Cryptographic Integrity

Receipts signed using:
	•	Ed25519 private key
	•	Canonical JSON serialization

Ensures:
	•	Tamper detection
	•	Non-repudiation
	•	Independent verification

⸻

5.3 Failure Modes

If policy fails:
	•	No order forwarded
	•	No escrow interaction
	•	No settlement
	•	Failure reason logged

Fail-closed model.

